        SELECT t.Id, t.AcquisitionCost, t.BarCode, t.CategoryId, t.DepartmentId, t.Description, t.ImageUrl, t.InventoryCost, t.InventoryQuantity, t.InventoryUnitMeas, t.MinimumInventoryQuantity, t.Name, t.Price, c.Id, c.DepartmentId, c.Description, c.Name, d.Id, d.Address, d.CNPJ, d.Name
        FROM 
        (
            SELECT p.Id, p.AcquisitionCost, p.BarCode, p.CategoryId, p.DepartmentId, p.Description, p.ImageUrl, p.InventoryCost, p.InventoryQuantity, p.InventoryUnitMeas, p.MinimumInventoryQuantity, p.Name, p.Price
            FROM Product AS p
            ORDER BY p.Id ASC
            OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
        ) AS t
        INNER JOIN Category AS c ON t.CategoryId == c.Id
        INNER JOIN Department AS d ON t.DepartmentId == d.Id

'queryContext => new SingleQueryingEnumerable<CategoryDTO>(
    (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
    RelationalCommandCache.QueryExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
            Id -> 0
            Name -> 1
            DepartmentName -> 2
            ProductCount -> 3
        SELECT c.Id, c.Name, d.Name AS DepartmentName, (
            SELECT COUNT(*)
            FROM Product AS p
            WHERE (c.Id != NULL) && (c.Id == p.CategoryId)) AS ProductCount
        FROM Category AS c
        INNER JOIN Department AS d ON c.DepartmentId == d.Id),

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`
